#

Classic Tuna Salad

10 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

fisheggdairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

quickhealthyeasysalad

Description

A simple and refreshing tuna salad that’s perfect for a light meal or snack.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 can (5 oz)
  • mayonnaise: 2 tbsp
  • celery, diced: 1/4 cup
  • red onion, diced: 2 tbsp
  • hard-boiled egg, chopped: 1
  • mixed greens: 2 cups
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • lemon juice: 1 tsp
